videos.description: Nick Ongenda tries to slam it home for DePaul, but Adama Sanogo flies in for a stellar block.

videos.headline: UConn's Sanogo soars to deny dunk attempt from behind

videos.description: Andre Jackson heaves a pass the length of the court to Adama Sanogo, who banks in a shot as the first-half buzzer expires.
